title: Paris attacker was Frenchman born in Chechnya
text:
Paris attacker was Frenchman born in Chechnya 11:14am EDT - 01:19
Police on Sunday scoured the background of a Frenchman born in Russia's Chechnya region who killed one man in a knife attack in Paris as the government said the 21-year old had been flagged previously as a potential security risk. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
